      <title>元大证券：美国大选结果改变投资周期观点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/us-election-changes-investment-cycle-perspective-yuanta-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[元大证券全球资产配置主管 Daniel Yoo 分享了他对美国和亚洲人工智能相关股票的看法，并讨论了美国总统大选结果将如何影响金融市场。他在“彭博社：亚洲交易”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/us-election-changes-investment-cycle-perspective-yuanta-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 01:47:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银 SuMi 的 Kobayashi 谈日本央行和日本市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/ubs-sumi-s-kobayashi-on-boj-japan-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银 SuMi TRUST 财富管理日本股票策略师 Chisa Kobayashi 在日本央行政策决定前讨论了她对日本市场的展望。她与 Shery Ahn 和 Haidi Stroud-Watts 就“彭博：亚洲交易”进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/ubs-sumi-s-kobayashi-on-boj-japan-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 01:38:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲投资级美元债券利差收窄至历史低位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/asian-investment-grade-dollar-bond-spreads-tighten-to-record-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国政策制定者采取一系列货币和财政刺激措施提升了亚洲债务的吸引力之后，亚洲顶级发行人的美元债券利差已收窄至历史最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/asian-investment-grade-dollar-bond-spreads-tighten-to-record-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 01:11:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将派特使赴华讨论电动汽车争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/eu-set-to-send-envoys-to-china-to-discuss-ev-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，欧盟已决定派官员前往北京举行更多会谈，旨在寻找对中国电动汽车征收关税的替代方案。彭博电视台记者刘敏敏报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/eu-set-to-send-envoys-to-china-to-discuss-ev-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 00:33:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大选紧张情绪推动避险需求，金价创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-as-us-election-jitters-drive-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国大选前的避险需求推动，且不受可能影响美联储今年降息规模的数据影响，金价攀升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/gold-xauusd-holds-near-record-as-us-election-jitters-drive-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 00:22:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电动汽车巨头之争中比亚迪销量首次超越特斯拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/byd-sales-beat-tesla-for-first-time-in-battle-of-ev-giants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国比亚迪股份有限公司公布季度营收，自两家公司在全球电动汽车销量上展开激烈竞争以来，首次超过特斯拉公司。彭博电视台的报道来自刘敏敏。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/byd-sales-beat-tesla-for-first-time-in-battle-of-ev-giants</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 00:17:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价延续涨势，因美国库存下降和中东局势受关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国原油库存减少后，油价连续第二个交易日上涨，市场关注中东地区可能出现的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 23:30:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市下跌，科技股拖累美国期货：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于强劲的经济数据使美联储即将降息的前景变得模糊，美国股市和政府债券下跌，亚洲股市周四下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 22:37:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃利奥特在停战后将西南航空的利息提高至 11.3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/elliott-slightly-boosts-southwest-airlines-interest-after-truce</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与西南航空公司达成停战协议后，埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 将其在西南航空公司的经济持股比例小幅提高至 11.3%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/elliott-slightly-boosts-southwest-airlines-interest-after-truce</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 20:05:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>必和必拓撤回关于放弃英美资源集团收购的评论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/bhp-retreats-from-comments-about-moving-on-from-anglo-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团被迫收回关于已“放弃”英美资源集团收购案失败的评论，以防止其受到英国收购委员会的束缚而无法再次发起收购尝试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/bhp-retreats-from-comments-about-moving-on-from-anglo-bid</guid>
